'''Symponiks''' were epic historical [[Music/Legends|musical]] works composed by [[Gungan/Legends|Gungans]] that were one of the pillars of Gungan oral history. Major events in Gungan history, both triumphant and tragic, inspired and formed the basis of the symponiks. [[Musikagung]]s performed such works at Boss coronations, Sacred Feasts, and other major events in Gungan life. The "[[Symponika Crunchen-Grand]]," composed by [[Beezar Pert/Legends|Beezar Pert]], became the definitive symponik of the formation of the [[Gungan Grand Army/Legends|Gungan Grand Army]].

